<h2>Fares&nbsp;frozen from January&nbsp;2020</h2>

<ul>
	<li>All <a href="/fares/find-fares/bus-and-tram-fares">fares on buses and trams</a></li>
	<li>All single <a href="/fares/how-to-pay-and-where-to-buy-tickets-and-oyster/pay-as-you-go">pay as you go</a> fares and <a href="/fares/how-to-pay-and-where-to-buy-tickets-and-oyster/single-and-return-tickets">paper single tickets </a>on Tube and DLR services</li>
