	<li>All fares on <a href="/fares/find-fares/emirates-air-line-fares">Emirates Air Line</a></li>
	<li>Certain fares on <a href="/modes/london-overground/index">London Overground</a> and <a href="/modes/tfl-rail/index">TfL Rail</a></li>
	<li>Certain fares on <a href="/modes/river/about-river-bus">River Bus</a></li>
</ul>

<p><a href="/fares/find-fares/tube-and-rail-fares/caps-and-travelcard-prices">Travelcard prices</a>, daily and weekly <a href="/fares/find-fares/tube-and-rail-fares/caps-and-travelcard-prices">caps</a> are set together&nbsp;with Train Operating Companies and not solely by the Mayor.</p>
